        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «كَانَ أَبِي عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَقِفُ بِالْمَشْعَرِ اَلْحَرَامِ حَيْثُ يَبِيتُ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2983 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"My father (as) used to stand at Al-Mash'ar al-Haram where he would spend the night.\""
